---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="CommercialPermits — Building Permit & Contractor License Data">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-12">
    <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-16 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
          <span class="inline-block bg-[rgba(229,183,60,0.12)] text-[#E5B73C] font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">
            ⚡ Coming Soon
          </span>
          <span class="inline-block bg-[rgba(16,185,129,0.12)] text-[#10B981] font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">
            June 2026 Tracking
          </span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-['Manrope'] text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-[#2D2D2D] mb-4">
          Thalux <span class="text-[#E5B73C]">CommercialPermits</span><br />
          Permit &amp; License Data
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[#333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Aggregated commercial building permit filings, mechanical permit records, and contractor license data from municipal and state data feeds across all 50 states. Every record includes permit type, valuation, square footage, contractor info, and current status — linking permits to licensed contractors for a complete construction intelligence picture.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#666] leading-relaxed">
          Stop navigating 3,200+ separate municipal permitting portals and inconsistent data formats. This is the same data, aggregated and normalized, at a fraction of the research overhead.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 md:mt-0">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-3xl text-[#E5B73C]">1.2M+</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[#666] mt-1">Permit Filings</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-3xl text-[#E5B73C]">24</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[#666] mt-1">Data Columns</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-3xl text-[#E5B73C]">3,200+</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[#666] mt-1">Municipalities</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-3xl text-[#E5B73C]">Monthly</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[#666] mt-1">Refresh Cadence</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-[#999] text-center">Data aggregated from municipal open-data feeds and state contractor boards. Enriched by Thalux AI.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Friction Teardown -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 border-t border-b border-[#DED8D0]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] text-center mb-10">The Permitting Data Maze</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-8 bg-white">
          <h3 class="font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-lg text-[#2D2D2D] mb-3">🧩 The Old Way</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[#666]">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#DED8D0] shrink-0">•</span> Navigate 3,200+ separate municipal permitting portals</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#DED8D0] shrink-0">•</span> Parse inconsistent data formats — PDF, HTML tables, proprietary APIs</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#DED8D0] shrink-0">•</span> Cross-reference contractor licenses across 50 state boards</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#DED8D0] shrink-0">•</span> Manually deduplicate permits issued under multiple trade codes</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 font-semibold text-[#2D2D2D]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] shrink-0">→</span> Estimated: 80+ hrs / month in research overhead</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="border-2 border-[#E5B73C] rounded-xl p-8 bg-white shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-lg text-[#2D2D2D] mb-3">⚡ CommercialPermits Dataset</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[#666]">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#10B981] shrink-0">✓</span> Aggregated from municipal open-data feeds and state contractor boards</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#10B981] shrink-0">✓</span> Normalized schema — one CSV, one standard for all jurisdictions</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#10B981] shrink-0">✓</span> Linked permits → contractor licenses for cross-verification</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#10B981] shrink-0">✓</span> Monthly refresh with change-log tracking</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 font-semibold text-[#2D2D2D]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] shrink-0">→</span> Your cost: one CSV download, zero portal navigation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Schema Table -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-2">Exact Schema (24 columns)</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] mb-8">Download the <a href="/data/commercial-permits/sample.csv" class="text-[#E5B73C] underline">free sample</a> to inspect before purchasing. Each permit is linked to the licensed contractor through contractor license number and state board verification.</p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-[#2D2D2D] text-white">
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Column</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Description</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Example</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">permit_id</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Unique municipal permit ID</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">BLD-2026-047193</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">permit_type</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Building, Mechanical, Electrical, Plumbing</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Commercial Building</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">municipality</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Issuing city or county</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Phoenix</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">state</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">State abbreviation</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">AZ</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">fips_code</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">County FIPS code</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">04013</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">issue_date</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Date permit issued</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">2026-06-10</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">status</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Issued, In Review, Closed, Expired</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Issued</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">project_description</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Brief scope of work</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Tenant fit-out — 3rd floor office</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">valuation</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Estimated project valuation ($)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">$1,250,000</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">square_feet</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Total square footage affected</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">8,500</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">property_address</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Project site address</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">2400 E Camelback Rd</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">parcel_id</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Assessor parcel number</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">126-09-001A</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">contractor_name</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Primary contractor on permit</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Desert Sky Construction Inc.</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">contractor_license</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">State contractor license number</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">AZ ROC-347812</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">contractor_class</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">License classification code</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">A - General Engineering</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">license_expiry</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Contractor license expiration</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">2027-03-31</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">license_status</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Active, Expired, Suspended</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Active</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">extracted_at</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">ISO 8601 extraction timestamp</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">2026-06-30T03:00:00Z</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Data Preview Grid -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 border-t border-b border-[#DED8D0]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-2">Sample Records</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] mb-8">5 of 1.2M+ records shown below. Full dataset extends orders of magnitude deeper.</p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-[#DED8D0] bg-white">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-[#2D2D2D] text-white">
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Permit ID</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Type</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Municipality</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">State</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Issue Date</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Valuation</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Status</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">BLD-2026-047193</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Building</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Phoenix</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">AZ</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-06-10</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">$1.25M</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">Issued</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">MEC-2026-021845</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Mechanical</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Nashville</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">TN</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-06-08</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">$340K</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">Issued</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">BLD-2026-047194</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Building</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Denver</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">CO</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-06-05</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">$4.8M</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#10B981]">Closed</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">ELC-2026-091237</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Electrical</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Charlotte</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">NC</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-06-03</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">$185K</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">Issued</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">BLD-2026-047195</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Building</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Seattle</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">WA</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-05-28</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">$2.1M</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">In Review</td></tr>
            <!-- Blur overlay rows -->
            <tr class="relative" style="filter: blur(4px); -webkit-filter: blur(4px); user-select: none;">
              <td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">PLM-2026-031244</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Plumbing</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Austin</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">TX</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-05-25</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">$95K</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">Issued</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="relative" style="filter: blur(4px); -webkit-filter: blur(4px); user-select: none;">
              <td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">MEC-2026-021846</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Mechanical</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Orlando</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">FL</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-05-22</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">$210K</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">In Review</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <div class="text-center py-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#FAFAF8] to-white">
          <span class="text-[#999] text-sm">+ 1.2M additional records across 3,200+ municipalities</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Launch Pricing -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] text-center mb-2">Launch Pricing</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] text-center max-w-lg mx-auto mb-10">Get notified when this dataset becomes available.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-[#E5B73C] transition-colors">
          <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-lg text-[#2D2D2D] mb-2">One-Time Snapshot</div>
          <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-4xl text-[#2D2D2D] mb-1">$49 <span class="text-base font-medium text-[#666]">USD</span></div>
          <div class="text-sm text-[#666] mb-6">One-time purchase</div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Full dataset CSV</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Point-in-time snapshot</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Single commercial license</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Immediate digital delivery</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-[#E5B73C] rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-lg text-[#2D2D2D] mb-2">Monthly Subscription</div>
          <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-4xl text-[#2D2D2D] mb-1">$99 <span class="text-base font-medium text-[#666]">USD</span></div>
          <div class="text-sm text-[#666] mb-6">per month</div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Fresh data every 30 days</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Incremental change log</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Preferential email support</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Cancel anytime — keep last snapshot</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Waitlist Signup -->
  <section id="waitlist" class="bg-white py-16 border-t border-[#DED8D0]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <div class="bg-[#F5F4F0] rounded-xl border border-[#DED8D0] p-10 md:p-12 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-3">
          Get Notified at Launch
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#666] max-w-md mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          CommercialPermits is in development. Leave your email and we'll notify you when it's ready.
        </p>
        <form name="permits-waitlist" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/data/govcon-intel/success" class="max-w-md mx-auto text-left">
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="permits-waitlist" />
          <p class="hidden">
            <label>Don't fill this out if you're human: <input name="bot-field" /></label>
          </p>
          <div class="mb-4">
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-1">Work Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-md text-sm focus:outline-none focus:border-[#E5B73C] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#E5B73C] bg-white"
              placeholder="you@company.com" />
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <label for="permit_type" class="block text-sm font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-1">Permit Type Interest <span class="text-[#999] font-normal">(optional)</span></label>
